HEADWORD: Eldership
<hw>Eld"er*ship</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <def>The
state of being older; seniority.</def> ⟦ldquo⟧Paternity an
<xex>eldership</xex>.⟦rdquo⟧ <rj><au>Sir W. Raleigh.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
